OL,5, Every household in the UK is to get an 
OL,6, energy bill discount of #400 this      
OL,7, October as part of a package of new    
OL,8, measures to tackle soaring prices.     
OL,10,FThe poorest households will also get a 
OL,11,Fpayment of #650 to help with the cost  
OL,12,Fof living, Chancellor Rishi Sunak said.
OL,14,FIt follows warnings that millions could
OL,15,Fbe left struggling if energy prices    
OL,16,Frise again in October as expected.     
OL,18,FMr Sunak said he had offered           
OL,19,F"significant support" for households   
OL,20,Fwho were facing "acute distress".      
